These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, dahlia
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, freelancer
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
2. the freelancer is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Flower   | dahlia  | tulip |
| Job       | musician | freelancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, aconite
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, brazilian
1. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
2. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Flower   | bellflower | aconite |
| Nationality      | brazilian     | pakistani  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, subway
2 different pets are kept: hamster, dog
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Transport   | van | subway  |
| Pet   | hamster | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
