.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-20::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, ritmeester
There 2 different types of food: corn, strawberry
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person eating corn##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2     |
| Cigar   | ritmeester   | game |
| Food   | strawberry | corn   |

 